# Search Pattern

## Defaults

- Debounce input (≈200–400ms)
- Clear (×) control when non-empty
- Empty-results state distinct from empty-list state
- Keyboard-friendly focus

## Placement

Search lives in the list/table toolbar — predictable, not buried.

## Advanced

Filters as compact triggers; combine search + filters without resetting each other unexpectedly. Persist filter state in URL when the page is shareable and the repo already does so.

## Performance

Search server-side or against indexed columns for large datasets. Do not load entire tables to filter in memory unless the dataset is known small.
